    CsdlAnnotatable

    public class CsdlRecord
extends CsdlDynamicExpression
implements CsdlAnnotatable
    The edm:Record expression enables a new entity type or complex type instance to be constructed. A record expression contains zero or more edm:PropertyValue (See CsdlRecord )elements.
